                    <span>I wrote my senior thesis on Utopia and The Republic, illustrating the  common theme of what makes a Utopian culture.  Believe it or not, the  Cliffs Notes had the most original and best thought out analysis that I  read, AND BELIEVE ME I read a lot on Utopian Literature.  If you are  reading Utopia, I suggest the Cliffs Notes.</span>
                  
              
